which would be japanese for &quot;The War of Zajeer&quot;! it's a message in disguise, and toastie has pointed the way!<br />
<br />
--<br />
<br />
inconveniencing yourself severely for rp reasons is extremely lame. maybe .5% of the EQ population even roleplays, I haven't seen any, and for sure RP is dead among the high levels. RP driven suggestions should never be taken seriously by devs because RP is pretend, while game mechanics are real.<br />
<br />
the rp idea is stupid for these reasons:<br />
<br />
Vortex: right, only mobs in PoSky can &quot;fly&quot; due to that falling code is not in this zone and mobs can path on a z axis. mobs with wings that aren't root immune are rare anyway. about 95% of EQ's mobs are actually walking on dry land anyway.<br />
<br />
anchor: there is little reason to root anything underwater anyway because of how physics change so much. yes, I did pull hydrotha with snare warping back in the day. no, it wasn't pretty. powater is pretty suicidal for a wizard to run around pulling in. everyone for the most part hates xping in water zones as well. we only went to kedge old world because lguk/solb were mob barren at the time. again, what's the point?<br />
