The major point is the creature would be immune to dmg.. I did propose a varied timer as well that I think would prevent any real abuse and add some fun for those who tried to regroup.  If this can be abused, point out how..is the idea w/o merit, fine.. tell me why.. I'm open minded enuff to hear it .. <br /></div>
			
